n-names>Jae-Seon</given-names></name></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author"><name><surname>Han</surname><given-names>Young-Hoon</given-names></name></contrib><contrib contrib-type="author"><name><surname>Bae</surname><given-names>In Hwa</given-names></name><xref rid="c1-molcell-37-1-17-3" ref-type="corresp"><sup>*</sup></xref></contrib><aff id="af1-molcell-37-1-17-3">Division of Radiation Cancer Research, Korea Institute of Radiological &#x00026; Medical Sciences, Seoul 139-706, 
